data.description:
HOME SWEET HOME! This home is Desirably located within minutes of shopping, dining, and entertainment. Features 4 bedrooms, 2 baths, office, and a 2-car garage. No carpet throughout home featuring an open floor plan makes entertaining a breeze! Vaulted ceilings, endless upgrades, and tons of natural light are just a few things this beauty has to offer. The roof was replaced in 2021 and AC replaced in 2022. The backyard is great for entertaining has two fruit trees. Enjoy outdoor living on the covered patio overlooking the large backyard. This home is situated in a fantastic location, within a mile easy to nearby shopping, dining, financial services and entertainment. 
less than a mile from the new co-op, walking distance to school. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this amazing property your own!
